ˇÄvernacular.ê07,2ÄTheÑArtofVeneryÄbyWilliamTwiciorTwiti,
huntsmantoEdwardII,survivesinbothAnglo-NormanandEnglish
versions.ê05,3ÄItisashortprosetreatise(sevenpagesinprint)
thatglancesataspectsofseveraldifferenthuntsbutdealswith
noneingreatdetail.Itgivesmiscellaneousinformationrelating
tothehuntintheformofadialoguebetweenamasterhuntsman
