reflecttheorderinwhichtopicsmightoccurtothespeakersof
thedialogue-orperhapsdidoccurtothewriter.

ThenexttwoMiddleEnglishhuntingmanuals,theÑMasterofGameÄ
andtheÑBokeofHuntyngÄ,seemtohavebeenwrittenataboutthe
