RatioÄ.ê05,5ÄThethirty-onechaptersfromÑLivredechasseÄdescribe
the'nature'ofthebeastsfoundinEngland,thetypesandcare
ofhounds,andhowto'goinquest'forthehart.TheDuke
omittedthechaptersontrapping,ontheconductofthehuntsand
onanimalsnotfoundinEngland,butaddedfivenewchapters,
includinglivelyandcomprehensiveaccountsofthehuntsfordeer
andhareinastylewhichcametocharacterisetheEnglish
traditionofhuntingmanuals.HealsoadaptedGastonPhoebus's
