Äalreadyforgotten.

Itisnotpossibletodeterminefromtheexistingevidencethe
criteriaaccordingtowhichtheanimalswereclassified,butthey
werenotanyobviousdifferencesbetweentheanimals.Thebeasts
ofvenerydidnothaveequivalenteconomicvalue,theyarenot
alledible,theroedeerwasconsideredasgoodachaseasthe
