'argent'andthebuck'isnoweneson,&bereztalowe'(152),
whiletheboaratthefifthyearhas'faucewax'.Thereisno
similaritybetweenthefatofthesebeastsrecognisedtodaywhich
couldaccountfortheirbeinggroupedtogether.Finally,the
suggestionthattheclassificationwasbasedonalegal
distinction,reflectingthedifferentapplicationofforestlaw
tothedifferentanimals,mustalsoberejectedasitimposesa
regrouping(withthehart,roedeerandbuckclassedtogether)
whichisnotfoundinthehuntingmanuals.ê03,15Ä

Thetendencytocategorisedoesnotendwiththeprimary
classificationofbeastsasvenery,chaseandvermin.InTwiti's
text,theanimalsarefurtherdividedaccordingtosuch
characteristicsasthetypeoftheirfat,whethertheyare
trackedbyalimerbeforethehunt,andhowtheirskinis
removed.Sometimesthereisacombination(orconfusion)ofthe
urgetocategoriseandthedevelopmentofspecialistterminology;
thussomebeastsareclassifiedaccordingtotermsappliedto
them,butthesetermsthemselvesaretheresultofextreme
refinementsinthewaytheanimalisperceivedortreated.For
example,theclassificationofanimalsaccordingtowhetherthey
bearleatherorskindoesnotreflectanyqualitativebiological
characteristicofthepelt.Thedistinctionbetweenleatherand
skinisemployedtorationalisethedifferencebetweentheways
inwhichtheanimalsareskinned.Clearlytherehasbeena
reversalofthecauseandeffect;themethodofremovalhascome
todefinethedifferencebetweenleatherandskinbutisitself,
presumably,basedonanatomicalconstraints,orperhapsonthe
valueofthepelt.Itisreallytheselattercriteriawhich
distinguishskinfromleather,althoughthehuntingmanualsdo
notacknowledgethis.

IntheÑTretyseÄ,arushofquestionsaboutterminologyrevealsthe
samedesiretocategorise,thoughnotallthequestionsare
answered:

Howmanyvenesonezbene˛er?Ianswer,˛ehert,˛eboor,˛ehar.
Howmanywythinchase?Howmanyinquyrry?ﬁehert.Howmonyin
